  "text": "Better LR-(i.e. higher specificity) was reached for temocillin <12 mm + Rosco KPC-MBL confirm kit [CITATION_1] and temocillin <8 mm + Rosco KPC-MBL confirm kit [CITATION_2] . When applied on ertapenem NS isolates, these two strategies allowed for retaining less isolates (n = 50 and n = 52, respectively) for further testing than our strategies (n = 120 and n = 115) but missed from 16 (30.8%) to 23 (44.2%) of the 52 CPE.",
